Class SimpleLossNetwork

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Layer, ReferenceCounting, Serializable

    public class SimpleLossNetwork
extends SupervisedNetwork
    The basic supervised network archetype. The network has two inputs; the input and the examplar output. A given component is then evaluated on the input, and the resulting output is combined apply the exemplar output via the loss function.
